OL,6,FThe Lords standards watchdog found
OL,7,Fthat Meyer breached harassment rules
OL,8,Fwith the comments about Lord Dholakia
OL,9,Fthat had a "racial element", but "had
OL,10,Fno malicious or racist intention" in
OL,11,Fthe incident with Ribeiro-Addy.
OL,13,FMeyer is the 71-year-old widow of
OL,14,Fformer US ambassador Sir Christopher
OL,15,FMeyer.
