OL,3,CTory peer facing three-week suspension
OL,4,Cfor calling colleague 'Lord Poppadom'
OL,6,FBaroness Meyer said that she meant
OL,7,Fthis as a compliment and didn't
OL,8,Frealise it would be unwelcome.
OL,10,FShe told the watchdog she immediately
OL,11,Funderstood, from Ribeiro-Addy's body
OL,12,Flanguage, that, "Oh, gosh, I did the
OL,13,Fwrong thing".
OL,15,FIn a report published on Thursday, the
OL,16,FHouse of Lords Conduct Committee said:
OL,17,F"We have carefully considered the
OL,18,FCommissioner's report and his proposed
OL,19,Fsanction.
