OL,6,F"Taking all the relevant factors into
OL,7,Faccount, we endorse his recommended
OL,8,Fsanction, and accordingly recommend to
OL,9,Fthe House that Baroness Meyer be
OL,10,Fsuspended from the service of the
OL,11,FHouse for three weeks, and that she
OL,12,Fundertake bespoke behaviour training."
